    "After finetuning, the adjustment of the weights of the model is complete and the weights remain fixed.",
    "The model can now be deployed, e.g.",
    "as an executable program to run on a computer.",
    "Although the weights are fixed after finetuning, the model is still able to learn during operation with a user through incontext learning.",
    "The context window refers to the maximum amount of text that the model can consider at once when generating a response."
